info.name: Just Coffee
info.description: Serves 1 | do not understand the difference between cappuccino, frappuccino and other ccinos of the world? order your plain and simple desi coffee.

info.name: Americano
info.description: Serves 1 | espresso shot + hot water - a classic black coffee made by diluting 2 shots of espresso with hot water. Ideal those for who like a bold and robust coffee flavour without the intensity of an espresso. The coffee is made from 100% arabica house blend, freshly roasted in our own roastery. No added sugar and suitable for vegans.

info.name: Cappuccino
info.description: Serves 1 | espresso shot + steamed milk + milk foam - the cappuccino has equal proportions of espresso, steamed milk and milk foam and is usually less sweeter than a cafe latte. Ideal for those who like a balanced flavour profile - the richeness from the espresso, creaminess from the milk, and lightness from the foam. The coffee is made from 100% arabica house blend, freshly roasted in our own roastery. No added sugar.

info.name: Cafe Latte
info.description: Serves 1 | espresso shot + steamed milk + milk foam - the cafe latte has a higher proportion of milk-to-cofee ratio with a thin layer of milk foam on top and is usually sweeter than a cappuccino. Ideal for those who like a mild flavour profile and a creamy and mellow coffee experience. The coffee is made from 100% arabica house blend, freshly roasted in our own roastery. No added sugar.

info.name: Cafe Mocha
info.description: Serves 1 | espresso shot + chocolate syrup + steamed milk - cafe mocha has equal proportions of coffee-to-chocolate-to- milk ratio. Ideal for those who like a swwet flavour profile with a smooth finish. The coffee is made from 100% arabica house blend, freshly roasted in our own roastery. No added sugar.

info.name: Flat White
info.description: Serves 1 | ristretto shot + steamed milk + milk foam - a flat white has a higher proportion of coffee-to-milk ratio since it is made using 2 ristretto shots (more concentrated coffee) rather than an espresso shot. Ideal for those who like a strong yet sweet flavour profile with a smooth finish. The coffee is made from 100% arabica house blend, freshly roasted in our own roastery. No added sugar.

info.name: Lemon Ginger Tea
info.description: Serves 1 | a soothing caffeine-free drink,lemon ginger tea is made by brewing green tea with fresh ginger, lemon and is lightly sweetened with honey. No added sugar or milk.

info.name: Himalayan Green Tea
info.description: Serves 1 | organic fresh green tea and rich in antioxidants. No added sugar or milk. Suitable for vegans.

info.name: Assam Tea
info.description: Serves 1 | a robust and bold black tea with a rich, malty flavor, hailing from the lush tea gardens of assam, india. No added sugar or milk. Suitable for vegans.

info.name: Darjeeling Tea
info.description: Serves 1 | the champagne of teas, with delicate floral notes and a crisp, refreshing taste. No added sugar or milk. Suitable for vegans.

info.name: Earl Grey
info.description: Serves 1 | classic black tea infused with the fragrant essence of bergamot oranges. No added sugar or milk. Suitable for vegans.
